<h2 id="the-passepartout">The Passepartout:</h2>

<ol>
  <li>
\[\frac{\partial b^\intercal a}{\partial a} = b\]
  </li>
  <li>
\[\frac{\partial a^\intercal A a}{\partial a} = (A^\intercal + A)a\]
  </li>
  <li>
\[\frac{\partial \log (\det A) }{\partial A}= (A^{-1})^\intercal\]
  </li>
  <li>
\[\frac{\partial tr(BA)}{\partial A}= B^\intercal\]
  </li>
</ol>

